<HEAD>Woman Jumps From Apartment, Kills Son</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MILAN, Italy (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A Tunisian woman abandoned by her husband
grabbed her three children and jumped from her apartment Friday,
killing her 1-year-old son and injuring herself and her two
daughters, authorities said.
   A social worker called on Dalila Ayari, but the woman locked
herself and the children on the fourth-floor balcony.
   Firefighters spread nets below the balcony in case the woman
jumped, but Mrs. Ayari, 32, ran to the other side of the apartment,
opened the window, grabbed the children and jumped with them into
the courtyard, police said.
   Mrs. Ayari and her daughters _ Anesa, 3, and Ahlem Monica, 5 _
were hospitalized in serious condition, while 1-year-old Omar died,
authorities said.
